SUMMARY:Cybersecurity Maturity Model Certification (CMMC)
DESCRIPTION:The Cybersecurity Maturity Model Certification (CMMC) requirements can be scary\, but this webinar will walk you step-by-step through the basic processes. As CMMC certification is required for Department of Defense (DoD) contracting\, this presentation will provide an overview of CMMC\, walk you through the initial certification requirements\, and provide you with the resources to make this journey far less overwhelming. We will provide resources and handouts to support your businesses efforts in becoming CMMC compliant. \nThis APEX Accelerator is funded in part through a cooperative agreement with the Department of Defense.
URL:https://wvbusinesslink.com/event/cybersecurity-maturity-model-certification-cmmc/
LOCATION:Zoom Webinar
CATEGORIES:Cybersecurity,Government,Webinar
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://wvbusinesslink.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/New-RCAC-Logo-7-12-23-1.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="RCAC APEX Accelerator":MAILTO:kpriddy@rcacwv.com
END:VEVENT
