SUMMARY:Trailblaze – Welcome Reception
DESCRIPTION:[vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css=”” css_params=””]Trailblaze is a dynamic one-day conference designed for early-stage\, high-growth startups and the people who support them. Hosted by TechConnect West Virginia and the WV Investor Collaborative\, Trailblaze connects founders\, funders\, and innovation champions to help shape the future of entrepreneurship in West Virginia. \nWhether you’re building an MVP\, hiring your first employee\, or pitching your startup story for the first time — this day is built for you. \nThrough real talk from successful founders\, investor insights\, and community-building opportunities\, Trailblaze helps high-growth entrepreneurs make smarter decisions and stronger connections.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]
URL:https://wvbusinesslink.com/event/trailblaze-welcome-reception/
