SUMMARY:UC Business Accelerator Program - Cohort 6 - Day 1
DESCRIPTION:At the UC Downtown Innovation Hub (DIH)\, we know you strive to be a sophisticated business owner. To achieve this\, you need a systematic approach to growing your business. The problem is that there are many hats to wear which makes you feel like you are not keeping up\, let alone getting ahead. We know you started your business with a passion for what you do. We know you want to grow your business into the vision that inspired your startup. Life is too short for that passion and vision to be drowned out by the constant struggle to stay on top of your competing responsibilities. We can relate. After working with dozens of growth companies from startups to multi-million-dollar enterprises\, we have developed a systems approach that brings clarity to business management\, enabling you to scale up and grow your business. \nListed below is the link needed for the application!
URL:https://wvbusinesslink.com/event/uc-business-accelerator-program-cohort-6-day-1/
LOCATION:UC Downtown Innovation Hub\, 240 Capitol Street\, Charleston\, WV\, 25301\, United States
CATEGORIES:Business Training
ORGANIZER;CN="UC Downtown Innovation Hub":MAILTO:innovate@ucwv.edu
GEO:38.3505388;-81.6336083
